snippet.title: Cuboton - game trailer
snippet.description:
New Top-Down Shooter game. Add to the wishlist
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1866340/Cuboton/

You are ordered to destroy a secret laboratory on the planet Cuboton. Complete the mission by fighting hordes of mutated creatures and find out what caused their existence.

All rights reserved
